data.text:
Torrent Cables Limited is a cable manufacturer company based in Ahmedabad, India.

Torrent Cables is one of the market leaders in HT Power Cable segment with a manufacturing capability of up to 132 kV XLPE Cables. It merged with Torrent Power in 2015.
